        <h1>Agenda Screening Services is the market leader in pre-employment and background screening.</h1>
        <p>Founded in 1996 we have built and maintained a wide and impressive spectrum of clients throughout the UK and Europe. <a href="/about">Learn more here</a></p>
        <h2 class="hide-for-medium-only">Why screen?</h2>
        <p class="hide-for-medium-only">It has never been more important for employers to have in place an effective and robust pre-employment screening programme. Agenda provides a range of pre-employment services and support initiatives, designed to help our customers win the battle against the enemy within, before, rather than after they have been compromised. <a href="/agenda-cms/uploads/pages/about/WhyScreen.pdf">Find out more here</a></p>
